# Mailing List & Admin Portal Plan

## Goal
Add a mailing list subscription feature to the main website and creating an admin portal to view collected emails.

## User Review Required
> [!IMPORTANT]
> **Data Storage**: For this V1 implementation on local/Vercel (serverless), we will use a JSON file (`data/emails.json`) for simplicity. **Note:** On Vercel (Production), local filesystem writes are ephemeral. If you deploy this, we should switch to a real database (Postgres/Supabase) or an external service (Mailchimp/ConvertKit). For now, `emails.json` works for local demo.

> [!CAUTION]
> **Security**: The Admin Portal will be password protected with a simple PIN for now to prevent public access.

